trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> and <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" /> events.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce i dati per gli eventi <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged" /> e <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties change.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs> classe viene utilizzata per la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> e <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classi quando i valori del <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> Modifica proprietà.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> property to get the previously assigned child control or element.
trans-unit.target: Utilizzare il <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> proprietà da ottenere il controllo figlio assegnata in precedenza o un elemento.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: Valore della proprietà <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> prima del nuovo valore assegnato.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inizializza una nuova istanza della classe <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene il valore della proprietà <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> prima del nuovo valore assegnato.

trans-unit.source: The value of the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> property before the new value was assigned.
trans-unit.target: Valore della proprietà <see cref="P:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child" /> prima del nuovo valore assegnato.
